fields.description:
In Beta  >= v1.6.7001 the Help/Check for Updates option is broken.

This is because of a change to the installer files, that mis-named the update checker's .ini file as 
{code}
SourceTreeUpdate.ini (x)
{code}
It should be
{code}
SourceTreeBetaUpdate.ini (x)
{code}

A potential workaround to simply rename the file 
{code}
c:\program files (x86)\atlassian\sourcetree beta\sourcetreeupdate.ini
{code}
to
{code}
c:\program files (x86)\atlassian\sourcetree beta\sourcetreebetaupdate.ini
{code}
corrects the error, but as yet does not seem to correctly pick up new updates.
